{
  "texts": [
    "We then compared the outcome with human tags and found that GPT-4o and Deepseek R1 and V3",
    "outperformed the other LLMs and were close enough in performance.",
    "Figure 3, taken from Table B1 shows agreement level and Cohen's Kappa for the agreement between expert human annotators and the LLM.",
    "The Cohen's Kappa is above 0.6 for GPT-4o and Deepseek models, which puts the agreement at the \"substantial\" level, as noted in extant research (e.g., Cohen 1960, McHugh 2012).",
    "Even though Deepseekchat was significantly cheaper than GPT-4o, Deepseek only provides a throughput of about 80 tokens per second."
  ]
}